http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/Oil-conservation-fortnight-observed/article14022521.ece

HPCL New White Oil Terminal located at Petro Park here has initiated various environment-friendly activities and adopted sustainability path on their premises as part of oil and gas conservation fortnight.The terminal team organised elocution, painting and slogan competitions for the students of Zilla Parishad High School, Gajuwaka, on Tuesday.Senior Installation Manager D. Rama Rao explained the importance of conservation of natural resources and advised the future generation representatives to take various activities in day-to-day life for better future.